{"lang": "ja_JP", "eventid": "story_kichi_set_1", "eventName": "幸運はすぐそばに", "entryType": "NONE", "storyCode": null, "avgTag": "幕間", "storyName": "幸運はすぐそばに", "storyInfo": "ヤクザの策に陥れられた吉星は、鍛冶町を離れる決断を強いられ、一軒ずつ隣人たちに挨拶をした。しかし彼女が旅立つよりも先に、彼女を陥れたヤクザに面倒が降りかかったようだ。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "64_g15_higashiroom", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$m_dia_street_intro", "key": "$m_dia_street_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "そう広くない室内に、パチンコ台がずらりと並んでおり、部屋の奥からは、ボタンを押す音とゲーム内の爆発音が連続して聞こえてくる。"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$doorknockquite"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1907_1#1$1", "duration": 2.0}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1897_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "お客さん、見ない顔だね。", "name": "吉星"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1897_1#1$1"}, {"id": 20, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1897_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "台は全部電源入ってるから、コインを入れりゃ遊べるよ。ドリンクとスナック菓子は自分でカウンターまで取りに来て――", "name": "吉星"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1897_1#1$1"}, {"id": 22, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1907_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "アンタが吉星か？", "name": "冷静なヤクザ"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1907_1#1$1"}, {"id": 24, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1897_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ありゃ、パチンコしに来たわけじゃなさそうだね？", "name": "吉星"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1897_1#4$1"}, {"id": 26, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1907_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ここは他の業務も引き受けていると聞いた。少し手伝ってもらいたい。", "name": "冷静なヤクザ"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1907_1#1$1"}, {"id": 28, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1897_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "えー、あたしが他に何の業務を引き受けられるっての？　人違いなんじゃ……", "name": "吉星"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1897_1#5$1"}, {"id": 30, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1907_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "親分がサルゴンから新しく仕入れた宝石について、アンタに見てもらいたいんだ……きちんとやり遂げれば、報酬はこれくらいだ。", "name": "冷静なヤクザ"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1907_1#1$1"}, {"id": 32, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ヤクザはハンドサインである数字を示した。"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1897_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ゴクリ……マジ……？", "name": "吉星"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1897_1#10$1"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1907_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ああ、間違いない。", "name": "冷静なヤクザ"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1907_1#1$1"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "64_g6_gokudouoffice", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ようこそ、吉星さん。", "name": "ヤクザの親分"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}, {"id": 48, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我々山川会はここ御机に来たばかりでね、市場開拓に手を貸してくれる現地の方が今すぐにでも欲しいのだよ。", "name": "ヤクザの親分"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}, {"id": 50, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1897_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "はいはい、そういう社交辞令はいいって。ブツはどこ？", "name": "吉星"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1897_1#2$1"}, {"id": 52, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ヤクザの親分が手招きすると、ずっしりした革製のケースが二人の間にある机に置かれた。"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_open_woodbox"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1897_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "こんなに……！？", "name": "吉星"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1897_1#6$1"}, {"id": 59, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "どれも、ある友人から買い取った天然の宝石だ。サイズも品質も極東では最高級と言えるだろう。", "name": "ヤクザの親分"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}, {"id": 61, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大枚を叩いて手に入れたはいいが、今度は処分に困っていてな……", "name": "ヤクザの親分"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "これほど多数の貴重品が一気に市場に流れてしまうと、本来あるべき価値が損なわれるだけではなく、その手の者の注目も引いてしまうだろう。", "name": "ヤクザの親分"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}, {"id": 65, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "吉星さんは宝石鑑定が得意な上に、御机で広い人脈を持っていると聞いてな。間違いなくいい買い手を見つけ、いい値段で売ってくれるだろうと思っている。", "name": "ヤクザの親分"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}, {"id": 67, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1897_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ちょ、まって！　まだ引き受けるって言ってないんだけど。", "name": "吉星"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1897_1#10$1"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "吉星はケースから適当に赤い宝石を拾い上げ、それを天井の照明にかざしてじっくり眺めた。"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1897_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一見良いモノに見えるけど、残念ながら……", "name": "吉星"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1897_1#2$1"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……残念ながら？", "name": "ヤクザの親分"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1897_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "サルゴンの宝石って確かに高品質なんだけど、あっちはだいたい手作りの小さい工房で作業してるから、一年の製造数がすっごい少ないんだよね。", "name": "吉星"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1897_1#1$1"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1897_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ここには一見色んな宝石があるように見える。でも、どれも加工技術がそっくりでしょ。", "name": "吉星"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1897_1#1$1"}, {"id": 79, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1897_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "カットがやけに整ってるし、どれも同じ工具で作ったみたいにそっくりでしょ。これらを手掛けたのがぺーぺーだって証拠だよ。", "name": "吉星"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1897_1#1$1"}, {"id": 81, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1897_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "こっち側も、加工が綺麗すぎる。良くて最近作られたばっかりの、悪い場合は……そもそも原石が天然石じゃない可能性もあるね。", "name": "吉星"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1897_1#4$1"}, {"id": 83, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "まさか……そんなはずがない！", "name": "ヤクザの親分"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}, {"id": 85, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "どれもオークション会場の倉庫から一つ一つ持ち出したのをこの目で見た上で、俺自身が一品ずつ選んだものだ。", "name": "ヤクザの親分"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}, {"id": 87, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1897_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "はぁ、信じられないってなら……これを見なよ。", "name": "吉星"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1897_1#4$1"}, {"id": 89, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1897_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "バルジャバンダバード博物館には、こいつと全く同じサファイアが所蔵されてる。「煌めきの涙」って名前の、ね。全く同じように、涙をかたどった黄金が嵌められてるんだ。", "name": "吉星"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1897_1#1$1"}, {"id": 91, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1897_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "サルゴンの国宝を、正規のオークションを通じてあたしらみたいな人間が手に入れられるって思う？", "name": "吉星"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1897_1#1$1"}, {"id": 93, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1897_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……それ以上はハッキリ言う必要ないでしょ？", "name": "吉星"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1897_1#1$1"}, {"id": 95, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "俺の宝石が……全部偽物だと言うのか？", "name": "ヤクザの親分"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}, {"id": 97, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1897_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ニセモノだね。誰が鑑定したって結論は変わらないよ。", "name": "吉星"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1897_1#1$1"}, {"id": 99, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……だがここにあるブツは全部、専門家が本物だと鑑定済みだ。", "name": "ヤクザの親分"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}, {"id": 101, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1897_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "は……？", "name": "吉星"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1897_1#2$1"}, {"id": 103, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "全部、とある議員サマが売ってくれたものでな。その方の名前は、極東のコレクション業界で知らない者などいないほどだ。", "name": "ヤクザの親分"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}, {"id": 105, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1897_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "それって、藤堂――", "name": "吉星"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1897_1#6$1"}, {"id": 107, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "おっと、口に出すなよ。", "name": "ヤクザの親分"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}, {"id": 109, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "あの方は宝石を俺に売る前に、わざわざ全部鑑定機関に送ってくださったんだ。ほら、専門家の鑑定結果はここにある。", "name": "ヤクザの親分"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}, {"id": 111, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ヤクザの親分は一冊の分厚いファイルを机に置いた。そのファイルには、様々な機関のロゴがプリントされている。"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1897_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（小声）*極東スラング*、どこもシャレにならない所ばっかじゃん……", "name": "吉星"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1897_1#2$1"}, {"id": 116, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "見ての通りだ。俺の宝石を偽物と言った専門家は一人もいない。吉星さん、君以外はな。", "name": "ヤクザの親分"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}, {"id": 118, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1897_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……より権威ある機関に鑑定してもらったのに、なんであたしを呼んだわけ？", "name": "吉星"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1897_1#2$1"}, {"id": 120, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "最初にはっきり言ったはずだ。君ならいい買い手を見つけてくれるだろうとな。", "name": "ヤクザの親分"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}, {"id": 122, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "事前に裏は取らせてある。君のお祖母さんは御机の宝石業界で長年名の知れた存在で、その事業は君が引き継いだそうだな。", "name": "ヤクザの親分"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}, {"id": 124, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "君が手を貸してくれるなら、こいつを売り捌くのは造作もないだろう。報酬についても、たっぷり用意する。心配は無用だ。", "name": "ヤクザの親分"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}, {"id": 126, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1897_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "あっはは……冗談でしょ？　あたしはただパチンコ屋を預かってるだけの普通の女だよ。そんなすごいことできるわけないじゃん？", "name": "吉星"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1897_1#1$1"}, {"id": 128, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……やはり俺のブツが偽物だと思っているから、手伝いたくない、と。", "name": "ヤクザの親分"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}, {"id": 131, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1897_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "えー、なにそれ？　ニセモノだなんてあたしは一度も言ってないって！", "name": "吉星"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1897_1#5$1"}, {"id": 133, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（手下を手招きする）", "name": "ヤクザの親分"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}, {"id": 135, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1907_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "はい、親分。全部録音しました。", "name": "冷静なヤクザ"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1907_1#1$1"}, {"id": 137, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1897_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 15.0, "ystrength": 15.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……ハメられた！？", "name": "吉星"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1897_1#6$1"}, {"id": 140, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "誠実な商売の基本をしただけさ。", "name": "ヤクザの親分"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}, {"id": 142, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "吉星さん、俺は君の能力を心から買っている。", "name": "ヤクザの親分"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}, {"id": 144, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "議員サマからこのブツを買い取って、俺は財産のほとんどを使い果たした。もしこいつを偽物だと鑑定するなら、俺はあっち側に報告書を持っていき、ことの始末をつけてもらう必要がある……", "name": "ヤクザの親分"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}, {"id": 146, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "だが、もしブツに問題がないなら……もちろん、俺の代わりにこの何億もする宝石を売り捌いてくれるだろう？", "name": "ヤクザの親分"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}, {"id": 148, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "64_g4_kajistreet_dusk", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$drift_intro", "key": "$drift_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1908_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "なあ、吉星がどこに行ったか知らないか？", "name": "困惑する住民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1908_1#1$1"}, {"id": 159, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1908_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "パチンコ屋が一日中閉まったままなんだ。かといってドアに張り紙もなかったし……", "name": "困惑する住民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1908_1#1$1"}, {"id": 161, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1911_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "なにか急用でもあったんじゃないかしら？　あの子、いつも忙しそうだし。", "name": "不思議そうな住民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1911_1#1$1"}, {"id": 163, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1908_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "はあ、今日は安いパチンコで遊べなさそうだな。ここの値段に慣れると、もうよそで打つ気にならないよ……", "name": "困惑する住民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1908_1#1$1"}, {"id": 165, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1897_1#10$1", "duration": 2.0}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1908_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "吉星！　戻ったのか！？", "name": "困惑する住民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1908_1#1$1"}, {"id": 171, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1897_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "はぁぁ……", "name": "吉星"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1897_1#10$1"}, {"id": 173, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1911_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ずいぶん落ち込んじゃってるわね。どうしたの？", "name": "不思議そうな住民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1911_1#1$1"}, {"id": 175, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1897_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "うん……あたしが警戒しなさすぎたよ。あんなこと、ハナから関わんなきゃよかった！", "name": "吉星"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1897_1#10$1"}, {"id": 177, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1897_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "あんな関わっちゃいけない人に行きつくなんて思わないじゃん……おかげで何億もするニセモノを代わりに売りさばくか、何億もする借金を背負うかの二択だよ！", "name": "吉星"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1897_1#8$1"}, {"id": 179, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1911_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1908_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "な、何億！？", "name": "二人の住民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1897_1#8$1"}, {"id": 183, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1897_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "このちっちゃい店を売っても……いや、あたし自身を売ってもそんな大金にならないっての！", "name": "吉星"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1897_1#8$1"}, {"id": 186, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "吉星は頭を叩きながら、ふらふら自分の店に戻っていく。驚く通行人だけがその場に残された。"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "夜が近づくと、こぢんまりした店の「吉星」と書かれた看板が不規則に弱々しく点滅する。まばたきの間に、ライトが完全に消えても不思議ではない。"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1897_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "吉星……ああ、吉星って名前なのに、なんでこんなにツイてないの……？", "name": "吉星"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1897_1#8$1"}, {"id": 191, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "64_g6_gokudouoffice", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1907_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "親分、ターゲットは家に戻ったようです。", "name": "冷静なヤクザ"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1907_1#1$1"}, {"id": 201, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "何か動きは？", "name": "ヤクザの親分"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}, {"id": 203, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1907_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ありません……抱き枕を抱いてひとしきり泣いた後、床をしばらく転がって、今はテレビゲームで遊んでいます。", "name": "冷静なヤクザ"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1907_1#1$1"}, {"id": 205, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……誰にも電話をしなかったか？", "name": "ヤクザの親分"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}, {"id": 207, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1907_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "していません。", "name": "冷静なヤクザ"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1907_1#1$1"}, {"id": 209, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1907_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "親分、もしかするとターゲットを間違えたのでは？　あのターゲットの家にはゲーム機以外目ぼしいものは何もなく、とても金持ちには思えないのですが……", "name": "冷静なヤクザ"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1907_1#1$1"}, {"id": 211, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "そんなはずがない！", "name": "ヤクザの親分"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}, {"id": 213, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "奴の祖母は昔、偽物の宝石を売ってボロ儲けしていたんだ。びた一文も孫娘に残さないなんてあり得るか？", "name": "ヤクザの親分"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}, {"id": 215, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "以前調査した時も、奴はそんな感じでだらだらしていただろう。金に困っていない証拠だ。", "name": "ヤクザの親分"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}, {"id": 217, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "こんな棚ぼた、他の奴らに譲ってたまるか！", "name": "ヤクザの親分"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}, {"id": 219, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$phone"}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 5.0}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1907_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ああ、私だ……なに？", "name": "冷静なヤクザ"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1907_1#1$1"}, {"id": 225, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1907_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……ああ、わかった。", "name": "冷静なヤクザ"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1907_1#1$1"}, {"id": 227, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$transmission", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1907_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "親分、見張りによると、ターゲットは荷造りをしているようです！", "name": "冷静なヤクザ"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1907_1#1$1"}, {"id": 232, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ふん、思った通りだ……しっかり見張っておけ、逃がすなよ。", "name": "ヤクザの親分"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}, {"id": 234, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "64_g5_kajistreet_d", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_758_1#1$1", "bstart": 0.2, "bend": 0.7}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "", "name": "？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_758_1#1$1"}, {"id": 244, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_758_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "日用品、アクセサリー、それに駄菓子も！　店内全品半額だよー！", "name": "熱心な屋台主"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_758_1#1$1"}, {"id": 246, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1897_1#1$1", "duration": 2.0}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_758_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "よお、吉星じゃないか。そんな大荷物背負ってどうしたんだ？", "name": "熱心な屋台主"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_758_1#1$1"}, {"id": 253, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1897_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "鈴木のおっちゃん、お別れしに来たんだ。あたし……しばらく鍛冶町にいれなくなっちゃった。", "name": "吉星"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1897_1#9$1"}, {"id": 255, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_758_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "はあ？　急に出ていくだなんて、何があったんだ？", "name": "鈴木のおっちゃん"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_758_1#1$1"}, {"id": 257, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1897_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "べ、別に何もないんだけど、ただ……そう、仕事の関係でさ。これからは別のところで仕事するんだ。", "name": "吉星"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1897_1#1$1"}, {"id": 259, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_758_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "そんなに急いで出るなんて、どんな仕事なんだよ……なあ吉星、何か面倒ごとに巻き込まれたとかじゃないだろうな？", "name": "鈴木のおっちゃん"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_758_1#1$1"}, {"id": 261, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_758_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "そういうことなら俺に話してくれ。何年もやってきたお隣さんじゃないか、絶対に手伝ってやるからさ。", "name": "鈴木のおっちゃん"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_758_1#1$1"}, {"id": 263, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1897_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（きょろきょろ見回す）なんていうか……確かにでっかい面倒ごとなんだけど、自己責任っていうか、みんなを巻き込みたくないっていうか。", "name": "吉星"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1897_1#10$1"}, {"id": 265, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1897_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "とにかく……そういうことで。", "name": "吉星"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1897_1#2$1"}, {"id": 274, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_759_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "吉星ちゃん、本当に悲しいわ……", "name": "悲しむ屋台主"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_759_1#1$1"}, {"id": 276, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_759_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "お祖母さんには生前本当にお世話になったし、あなたのこともずっと本当の妹だと思ってきたのよ。それなのに、こんな風に出ていってしまうなんて。", "name": "悲しむ屋台主"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_759_1#1$1"}, {"id": 278, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_759_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "それに、お店はどうするの……？", "name": "悲しむ屋台主"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_759_1#1$1"}, {"id": 280, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1897_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "パチンコ屋は鉄斎じいさんのもんだし、次の店番くらいきっと見つけてくれるよ。", "name": "吉星"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1897_1#2$1"}, {"id": 282, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1897_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "立地もいいし、あたしの店が二階にあったって、借りてくれる人はいるでしょ。ま、今後はビデオ屋とかラーメン屋とかになるかもだけど……", "name": "吉星"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1897_1#2$1"}, {"id": 284, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_759_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ぐすっ、吉星ちゃん、それ以上は言わないで……誰かがここで新しい店を開くなんて、わたし望んでないわ。ただあなたにずっと鍛冶町にいてほしいだけよ。", "name": "悲しむ屋台主"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_759_1#1$1"}, {"id": 286, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1897_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "で、でも……姉ちゃん、あたしもう行かなきゃ。", "name": "吉星"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1897_1#9$1"}, {"id": 288, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1908_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "なんでそんな急に出ていくんだ？　みんなに連絡するから、少なくとも送別会をやってから行けよ！", "name": "怒る屋台主"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1908_1#1$1"}, {"id": 297, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1897_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（きょろきょろ見回す）い、いいって！　明日にはもう出ていくから、みんなに手間をかけさせることないでしょ。", "name": "吉星"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1897_1#10$1"}, {"id": 299, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1907_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "冷静なヤクザ"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1907_1#1$1"}, {"id": 304, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "64_g6_gokudouoffice", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1907_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "吉星はきょう一日中外を歩き回って、一軒ずつ近所の住民に別れを告げていました。", "name": "冷静なヤクザ"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1907_1#1$1"}, {"id": 314, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1907_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "最初から私に気がついていたようで、鑑定の件も借金の件も口外していません。", "name": "冷静なヤクザ"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1907_1#1$1"}, {"id": 316, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ふん、何もできないことくらいわかっていたさ。", "name": "ヤクザの親分"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}, {"id": 318, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1907_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "もしかすると……後々金を借りるために手を打っているのかもしれませんね。", "name": "冷静なヤクザ"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1907_1#1$1"}, {"id": 320, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "寂れた街でしょぼい店をやっている店主どもに、何ができるというんだ？", "name": "ヤクザの親分"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}, {"id": 322, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "いつまで隠れていられるか、見ものだな……", "name": "ヤクザの親分"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}, {"id": 324, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "64_g10_higashigarden_r", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_758_1#1$1", "bstart": 0.2, "bend": 0.7}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……今日はもう終わりだ、遊ぶ気分じゃない。", "name": "？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_758_1#1$1"}, {"id": 334, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_758_1#1$1", "bstart": 0.2, "bend": 0.7}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "みんな、吉星のことは聞いたよな？", "name": "？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_758_1#1$1"}, {"id": 336, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_759_1#1$1", "bstart": 0.2, "bend": 0.7}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "あの子ったら、あんなに朝早くからお別れを言いにきたのよ。かわいそうに、あんなつらそうな顔をして……", "name": "？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_759_1#1$1"}, {"id": 338, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_758_1#1$1", "bstart": 0.2, "bend": 0.7}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "背後に誰がいるか、調べはついたか？", "name": "？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_758_1#1$1"}, {"id": 340, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1908_1#1$1", "bstart": 0.2, "bend": 0.7}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ここ数日、町では見慣れない顔が何人か、こっそり吉星の後ろをつけ回ってたよ。挙動を見た限り、その筋の人間だと思う。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1908_1#1$1"}, {"id": 342, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1908_1#1$1", "bstart": 0.2, "bend": 0.7}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "店じまいの時に、高橋と渡辺に後をつけさせておいた。まずはあいつらが何者かを掴まないと。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1908_1#1$1"}, {"id": 344, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_758_1#1$1", "bstart": 0.2, "bend": 0.7}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "よし、こっちは古いダチ何人かに連絡を取るつもりだ。", "name": "？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_758_1#1$1"}, {"id": 346, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1908_1#1$1", "bstart": 0.2, "bend": 0.7}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "おい、手を出すつもりなのか？", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1908_1#1$1"}, {"id": 348, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1908_1#1$1", "bstart": 0.2, "bend": 0.7}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "忘れたのか？　昔鉄斎さんの前で誓いを立てただろ、この町で平穏な余生を過ごす代わりに、きっぱり足を洗うって――", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1908_1#1$1"}, {"id": 350, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_759_1#1$1", "bstart": 0.2, "bend": 0.7}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "鉄斎さんはいま、あの二番手とやり合ってるんでしょ、吉星ちゃんを助けたいと思ってても、そんな余裕はないと思うわ。", "name": "？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_759_1#1$1"}, {"id": 352, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_759_1#1$1", "bstart": 0.2, "bend": 0.7}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "それに、うちの子がつらい目に遭ってるのよ。これでただ黙って見てたら、どんな顔をしてまた集まって遊べばいいの？", "name": "？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_759_1#1$1"}, {"id": 354, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1908_1#1$1", "bstart": 0.2, "bend": 0.7}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……それもそうだな。ここ十何年のんびりしすぎてたせいか、若い頃の棘がごっそり抜けちまってたよ……", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1908_1#1$1"}, {"id": 356, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_758_1#1$1", "bstart": 0.2, "bend": 0.7}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "茶番はもう十分だろう、やるぞ。", "name": "？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_758_1#1$1"}, {"id": 358, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "64_g15_higashiroom", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "せやけど――今もここで店を続けとるわけやろ。結局どないして解決したんや？", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4199_makiri_1#1$1", "duration": 2.0}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1897_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ああ、それが変な話でね。荷物をまとめて、最後は鉄斎じいさんにお別れしにいこうとしてたんだよ。そしたら家を出ようとしたとこで、あのヤクザたちが玄関を塞いで……", "name": "吉星"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1897_1#1$1"}, {"id": 373, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 375, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 377, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 378, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "64_g4_kajistreet_dusk", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 379, "prop": "cameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "keep": "true", "amount": 1.0, "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 381, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 382, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 383, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1907_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 384, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 15.0, "ystrength": 15.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 385, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（深々と頭を下げる）本当に――申し訳ございませんでした！", "name": "恐れるヤクザ&親分"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}, {"id": 386, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 387, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1897_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 388, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……え？", "name": "吉星"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}, {"id": 389, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 390, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（頭を下げたまま）吉星様、諫崎の松竹会とご関係があるとは露知らず……まことに失礼いたしました！", "name": "ヤクザの親分"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}, {"id": 391, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1897_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 392, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "は？　なにそれ？", "name": "吉星"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}, {"id": 393, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 394, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "当方の不手際についてはこの通り深く反省しております。何卒寛大なご処置を！", "name": "ヤクザの親分"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}, {"id": 395, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 396, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "こちら心ばかりのものですが、どうかお受け取りください！", "name": "ヤクザの親分"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}, {"id": 397, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 398, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（さらに頭を下げる）まことに――申し訳ございませんでした！", "name": "ヤクザの親分"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}, {"id": 399, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 400, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 401, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 402, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 403, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 404, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "64_g15_higashiroom", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 405, "prop": "cameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "keep": "true", "amount": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 406, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 407, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$calm_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 408, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 409, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1897_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 410, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "と、こんな感じでね。結局びた一文も賠償しなかったし、逆に宝石鑑定の報酬をがっつりもらっちゃったってわけ……ふふっ、すごいでしょ？", "name": "吉星"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1897_1#1$1"}, {"id": 411, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4199_makiri_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 412, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ほんま波乱万丈な話やな……誰が収めてくれたんか知りたいんやったら、代わりに調べとこか？", "name": "森内"}, "figure_art": "avg_4199_makiri_1#1$1"}, {"id": 413, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1897_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 414, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "いいって、そんなのハッキリさせてもしょうがないでしょ。", "name": "吉星"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1897_1#1$1"}, {"id": 415, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1897_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 416, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "助けてくれた優しいお方がずっと名乗り出てないのは、私に知ってほしくないってことじゃん。", "name": "吉星"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1897_1#4$1"}, {"id": 417, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1897_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 418, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "それに、ただあたしがツイてたってだけかもしれないからね――ほら見て、さっき神社で引いたおみくじ、「大吉」だって！", "name": "吉星"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1897_1#1$1"}, {"id": 419, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4199_makiri_1#13$1"}}, {"id": 420, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ふぅ――そない前向きなんやったら、もう心配いらんか。", "name": "森内"}, "figure_art": "avg_4199_makiri_1#13$1"}, {"id": 421, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1897_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 422, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "生きていけるんなら、どんな形で過ごしたっていいじゃん。その上で、ここで一生店をやっていけたらいいなって。あたしの望みはそれだけ！", "name": "吉星"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1897_1#1$1"}, {"id": 423, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4199_makiri_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 424, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "言うても、君にはご家族の遺した莫大な遺産があるんちゃうの？", "name": "森内"}, "figure_art": "avg_4199_makiri_1#3$1"}, {"id": 425, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1897_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 426, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "莫大な遺産って何のこと？", "name": "吉星"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1897_1#6$1"}, {"id": 427, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1897_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 428, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ばっちゃはずっとあたしに「人生は短くつらいものだからね、その時その時を楽しみなさい。」って言って、お金を稼ぐたびにいろんな所の旅行に連れてってくれたんだ。", "name": "吉星"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1897_1#1$1"}, {"id": 429, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1897_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 430, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "いま思い出すと、帰ってきたら、いつもご飯にありつけないくらい財布がすっからかんになってたけどね……", "name": "吉星"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1897_1#1$1"}, {"id": 431, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4199_makiri_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 432, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（汗を拭く）はあ、君がなんでこないな子になったんかようわかったわ。ならよけいこの店をやめんでよかったな……", "name": "森内"}, "figure_art": "avg_4199_makiri_1#4$1"}, {"id": 433, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1897_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 434, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "この店をやめるなんてありえないでしょ。あたしたちの家でもあるんだから、マジで畳んだら住むとこまでなくなっちゃうじゃん！　それくらいわかってるって！", "name": "吉星"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1897_1#1$1"}, {"id": 435, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 436, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 437, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_windchime_JP", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 438, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 439, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1897_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 440, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "おっと、お客さんが来た。台は全部電源入ってるから、コインを入れりゃ遊べるよ。ドリンクとスナック菓子は自分でカウンターまで取りに来て――", "name": "吉星"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1897_1#11$1"}, {"id": 441, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 442, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 443, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 444, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 445, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 446, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 447, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 448, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 449, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}